msContents.summary: Lacunose commentary on the grammar of al-Ajurrūmīyah by Ibn Ājurrum; a few leaves are missing and many leaves have had their edges repaired.

author.persName: Jibrīl, Zayn al-Dīn Muḥammad, active 15th century-16th century

supportDesc.extent: 100 partially foliated leaves : 172 x 130 (127 x 85) mm, bound to 172 x 138 mm

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in naskh in black ink; pointed.

decoDesc.decoNote: Rubrications in red; double border-rule in red.

origin.p: Copy completed on 4 Jumādá al-Ākhirah in the year 988 AH (June 1580) (f. [101]r)

history.provenance: Formerly owned by Muḥammad ʻAwwād ibn Ḥusayn Afandī (f. [101]v).
